</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-de7139d78 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_heading" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-de7139d78 mcb-item-heading-inner"><h2 class="title">With automation, comes
greater efficiency. </h2></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-81ec78a5d one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_list_2" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-81ec78a5d mcb-item-list_2-inner"><ul class="mfn-list mfn-list-left mfn-list-top"><li class="mfn-list-item" style="counter-set:my-sec-counter 0"><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Elevate your daily view </strong> with a best-in-class hotel reservation software calendar and modify stays with drag-and-drop upgrades.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Enable self-serve check-in</strong> , online check-in/out, and effortless upselling with a digital menu.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Create rate plans</strong>, customise packages, simplify group bookings, automate guest emails, and generate invoices with ease.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Generate powerful reports </strong>to stay informed about your revenue and operational performance.</span></li></ul>
</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-ec33c37c9 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-ec33c37c9 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="/platform/pms/"         title=""><span class="button_label">Learn more</span></a>
</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section mcb-section mfn-default-section mcb-section-9a1005d5c default-width wrap-reverse"   style="" ><div class="mcb-background-overlay"></div><div class="section_wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps mcb-section-inner mcb-section-inner-9a1005d5c"><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-1011123c9 one-second tablet-one-second laptop-one-second mobile-one clearfix" data-desktop-col="one-second" data-laptop-col="laptop-one-second" data-tablet-col="tablet-one-second" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-1011123c9 mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-96046d718 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_list_2" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-96046d718 mcb-item-list_2-inner"><ul class="mfn-list mfn-list-left mfn-list-middle"><li class="mfn-list-item" style="counter-set:my-sec-counter 0"><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Channel-manager-icon-1-2.webp#319410" /><noscript><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Channel-manager-icon-1-2.webp#319410" alt="" /></noscript></span><span class="mfn-list-desc">CHANNEL MANAGER</span></li></ul>
</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-074d06597 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_heading" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-074d06597 mcb-item-heading-inner"><h2 class="title">More visibility, 
fewer headaches.</h2></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-2c98c7fe0 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_list_2" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-2c98c7fe0 mcb-item-list_2-inner"><ul class="mfn-list mfn-list-left mfn-list-top"><li class="mfn-list-item" style="counter-set:my-sec-counter 0"><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Expand your reach </strong>and boost bookings through 200+ channels, including OTAs, metasearch engines, GDSs, and bedbanks.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Automate your pricing</strong> with easy-to-use dynamic pricing rules that respond to real-time market demand.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Keep inventory perfectly synced</strong> across all channels with our hotel software, eliminating overbookings and ensuring maximum visibility.</span></li></ul>
</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-7820332c4 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-7820332c4 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="/platform/channel-manager/"         title=""><span class="button_label">Learn more</span></a>
