</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-d4337daad one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_heading" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-d4337daad mcb-item-heading-inner"><h2 class="title">Direct bookings, 
more money.</h2></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-9c482ca23 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_list_2" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-9c482ca23 mcb-item-list_2-inner"><ul class="mfn-list mfn-list-left mfn-list-top"><li class="mfn-list-item" style="counter-set:my-sec-counter 0"><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Turn website visitors into guests </strong> with a high-converting, mobile-friendly hotel room booking software.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Boost revenue with bookable add-ons</strong> like picnic baskets, local tours, three-course meals or experiences.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Drive more direct bookings</strong> with a price checker and Google Hotels integration.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Run targeted promotions</strong> and encourage guest loyalty with discount codes and agent logins for smarter rate management.</span></li></ul>
</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-b8295cd24 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-b8295cd24 mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="/platform/booking-engine/"         title=""><span class="button_label">Learn more</span></a>
</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section mcb-section mfn-default-section mcb-section-cf29e1cca default-width wrap-reverse"   style="" ><div class="mcb-background-overlay"></div><div class="section_wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps mcb-section-inner mcb-section-inner-cf29e1cca"><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-47b20ed72 one-second tablet-one-second laptop-one-second mobile-one clearfix" data-desktop-col="one-second" data-laptop-col="laptop-one-second" data-tablet-col="tablet-one-second" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-47b20ed72 mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-7349dd15e one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_list_2" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-7349dd15e mcb-item-list_2-inner"><ul class="mfn-list mfn-list-left mfn-list-middle"><li class="mfn-list-item" style="counter-set:my-sec-counter 0"><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><img src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" alt="" data-lazy-src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/payments-icon-1-3.webp#319386" /><noscript><img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/payments-icon-1-3.webp#319386" alt="" /></noscript></span><span class="mfn-list-desc">PAYMENTS</span></li></ul>
</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-bbbc6fca1 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_heading" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-bbbc6fca1 mcb-item-heading-inner"><h2 class="title">Seamless transactions, greater guest satisfaction.</h2></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-bad8085f0 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_list_2" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-bad8085f0 mcb-item-list_2-inner"><ul class="mfn-list mfn-list-left mfn-list-top"><li class="mfn-list-item" style="counter-set:my-sec-counter 0"><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Send payment links </strong> to guests for quick and easy online payments on prepayments, deposits, or outstanding balances.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Enable contactless payments </strong> by offering online check-in and check-out for a seamless guest experience.</span></li><li class="mfn-list-item" ><span class="mfn-list-icon" ><i class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true" ></i></span><span class="mfn-list-desc"><strong>Monitor virtual credit cards (VCC)</strong> , automate charging and manage all OTA transactions in one centralised overview for seamless payment processing.</span></li></ul>
</div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-5def8429f one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-5def8429f mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="/platform/payments/"         title=""><span class="button_label">Learn more</span></a>
