	<li><a href="https://roomraccoon.co.uk/blog/blog-technology/" rel="category tag">Technology</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class="post-title"><h4 class="entry-title " itemprop="headline"><a href="https://roomraccoon.co.uk/blog/best-hotel-guest-messaging-apps/">Best Hotel Guest Messaging Apps 2026</a></h4></div><div class="post-excerpt">A guest messaging app is the difference between a modern guest journey that works for you and one that makes you work harder. Without it, your<span class="excerpt-hellip"> […]</span></div><div class="post-footer"><div class="button-love"><span class="love-text">Do you like it?</span></div><div class="post-links"><i class="icon-doc-text" aria-hidden="true"></i> <a href="https://roomraccoon.co.uk/blog/best-hotel-guest-messaging-apps/" class="post-more">Read more</a></div></div></div></div></article></div></div>
</div>
</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section mcb-section mfn-default-section mcb-section-1a91cb4ca default-width"   style="" ><div class="mcb-background-overlay"></div><div class="section_wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps mcb-section-inner mcb-section-inner-1a91cb4ca"><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-6c03a8fad one tablet-one laptop-one mobile-one clearfix" data-desktop-col="one" data-laptop-col="laptop-one" data-tablet-col="tablet-one" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-6c03a8fad mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-f3831473d one tablet-one laptop-one mobile-one mfn-nested-wrap clearfix" data-desktop-col="one" data-laptop-col="laptop-one" data-tablet-col="tablet-one" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-f3831473d mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-8922bd5e2 one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_heading" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-8922bd5e2 mcb-item-heading-inner"><h2 class="title">FAQs: Hotel Management Software </h2></div></div></div></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-81a2a995a one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_faq" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-81a2a995a mcb-item-faq-inner"><div class="faq"><div class="mfn-acc faq_wrapper  open1st"><div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">1</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>What is hotel management software and why is it important for hotels?</div><div class="answer">Hotel management software is an online platform that enables hotel owners to centralise and optimise all their daily operations. Think of reservation management, payments, invoicing, guest communication, and reporting. It is important for hotels because it reduces administrative burdens, minimises the risk of errors, and significantly enhances the guest experience.  </div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">2</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>How does hotel management software help automate reservations and payments in a hotel environment?</div><div class="answer">Hotel Management Software, such as RoomRaccoon, automates key processes, largely eliminating manual data entry. Reservations made through the hotel’s own website, OTAs (such as Booking.com and Airbnb), or by phone are immediately registered in the system. The PMS can handle payments via integrated payment solutions, automatically generate invoices, and securely store guest data. This saves time and reduces the chance of human errors.   </div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">3</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>What are the main features of hotel software or a PMS?</div><div class="answer"><ul>
  <li><strong>Reservation Management:</strong> Central management of all bookings.</li>
  <li><strong>Channel Manager:</strong> Automatic synchronisation of availability and rates on OTAs and other channels.</li>
  <li><strong>Invoicing & Payments:</strong> Automated invoices and payment processing.</li>
  <li><strong>Reporting:</strong> Insights into revenue, occupancy rates, Average Daily Rate (ADR), and more.</li>
  <li><strong>Guest Communication:</strong> Automated emails for confirmations, upselling, and feedback requests.</li>
  <li><strong>Housekeeping & Tasks:</strong> Real-time updates on room status and task assignments.</li>
</ul></div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">4</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>What benefits does hotel management software offer for small and medium-sized hotels?</div><div class="answer"><ul>
  <li><strong>Time Savings</strong>: Less manual work thanks to automation.</li>
  <li><strong>Cost Savings:</strong> One all-in-one system often replaces multiple separate tools.</li>
  <li><strong>Overview & Insight:</strong> All data in one dashboard, enabling quicker decision-making.</li>
  <li><strong>Professional Image</strong>: An automated system makes a professional impression on guests.</li>
  <li><strong>More Direct Bookings: </strong>Through an integrated booking engine on the hotel’s own website.</li>
</ul></div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">5</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>Can a hotel management system be linked to OTAs such as Booking.com and Airbnb?</div><div class="answer">Yes, with a Channel Manager (part of many PMS solutions, including RoomRaccoon), it is possible to directly connect to external booking channels. All rates, availability, and reservations are automatically synchronised, preventing double bookings and ensuring you always work with up-to-date data </div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">6</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>How does hotel software improve the guest experience and a hotel’s efficiency?</div><div class="answer">By automating processes and centralising data. Staff have immediate insight into guest information, ensuring smooth check-ins and check-outs. Automated emails and upselling options enhance the guest experience. Moreover, the software allows rapid responses to questions or requests, which increases overall guest satisfaction.   </div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">7</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>What reports and insights does hotel management software provide for better decision-making?</div><div class="answer"><p>A PMS typically offers various dashboards and reports that provide insights into:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Revenue, ADR, and RevPAR</li>
  <li>Occupancy rates</li>
  <li>Booking sources (through which channels do guests arrive?)</li>
  <li>Cost overviews</li>
  <li>Guest data and repeat bookings</li>
</ul>
<p>This data helps in making strategic decisions, such as:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Pricing strategies</li>
  <li>Marketing efforts</li>
  <li>Staff planning</li>
</ul></div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">8</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>Is hotel software secure and does it comply with privacy regulations (GDPR)?</div><div class="answer">Modern PMS solutions, including RoomRaccoon, comply with GDPR and other relevant legislation. This means that personal data is encrypted, data transfer is secure (using SSL certificates), and only authorised users have access to the information. Often, there are also options for two-factor authentication and for restricting certain features to specific user roles.  </div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">9</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>How much does hotel management software cost and what subscription options are generally available?</div><div class="answer">Costs depend on the type of hotel (number of rooms, specific features) and the desired modules (channel manager, booking engine, upsell, etc.). Many providers work with monthly or annual subscriptions, sometimes supplemented by transaction fees per booking. RoomRaccoon, for example, offers various packages based on your needs and the size of your hotel. A transparent pricing model and a scalable subscription are usually the standard in the market.   </div></div>
<div class="question" tabindex="0" role="link"><div class="title"><span class="num">10</span><i class="icon-plus acc-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="icon-minus acc-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i>Why do hotels choose RoomRaccoon as their hotel management software (PMS)?</div><div class="answer"><ul>
  <li><strong>All-in-One Solution:</strong> PMS, Channel Manager, Booking Engine, Payments, and Revenue Management System (RMS) in a single platform.</li>
  <li><strong>User-Friendliness</strong>: The system is intuitively designed and easy to learn.</li>
  <li><strong>Innovation & Updates</strong>: RoomRaccoon is continuously developing and rolling out new features.</li>
  <li><strong>Customer Service:</strong> Personalised support and guidance during implementation and daily use.</li>
  <li><strong>Scalability</strong>: Suitable for both small boutique hotels and larger chains with multiple locations.</li>
</ul>
<p>
 By opting for an integrated solution like RoomRaccoon, you save time, reduce errors, and simultaneously enhance the guest experience.
 Ultimately, this leads to higher satisfaction among both hotel staff and guests, and improved revenue.
</p></div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="section mcb-section mfn-default-section mcb-section-947bc8936 default-width"   style="" ><div class="mcb-background-overlay"></div><div class="section_wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps mcb-section-inner mcb-section-inner-947bc8936"><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-6f06c99e5 one tablet-one laptop-one mobile-one clearfix" data-desktop-col="one" data-laptop-col="laptop-one" data-tablet-col="tablet-one" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-6f06c99e5 mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-7f39109d7 five-sixth laptop-five-sixth tablet-five-sixth mobile-one column_heading" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-7f39109d7 mcb-item-heading-inner"><h2 class="title">Trusted by 2000+ hoteliers worldwide, <em>start</em> now. </h2></div></div></div></div><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-3c4e58a54 one tablet-one laptop-one mobile-one clearfix" data-desktop-col="one" data-laptop-col="laptop-one" data-tablet-col="tablet-one" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-3c4e58a54 mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="wrap mcb-wrap mcb-wrap-6d042963d one-fifth tablet-one-fifth laptop-one-fifth mobile-one mfn-nested-wrap clearfix" data-desktop-col="one-fifth" data-laptop-col="laptop-one-fifth" data-tablet-col="tablet-one-fifth" data-mobile-col="mobile-one" style=""   ><div class="mcb-wrap-inner mcb-wrap-inner-6d042963d mfn-module-wrapper mfn-wrapper-for-wraps"  ><div class="mcb-wrap-background-overlay"></div><div  class="column mcb-column mcb-item-fe9a9dd5e one laptop-one tablet-one mobile-one column_button" style="" ><div class="mcb-column-inner mfn-module-wrapper mcb-column-inner-fe9a9dd5e mcb-item-button-inner"><a class="button  button_size_2" href="/demo/"         title=""><span class="button_label">Book a demo</span></a>
